; 祭壇の間
@saveon
[texton]
At the far end of the altar room was a large stone pillar, with a stone monument standing in front of it.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Is this...?」[k]
I brought my face close to the stone monument to read the words on it, when...[k]
[textoff]
@image layer=e0 mode=psdodge5 opacity=0 storage=screen_white visible=true
@move layer=e0 time=500 path=,,96
@wm
@wait time=1000
[texton]
∗pweeew∗[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
Suddenly, the surrounding walls began to glow![k]
The light fills the entire room with a gentle glow.[k]
[？？？ v=vp003 key=ポラリス f=polaris_99 buf=12]「You... have the blood of a demon hunter, do you not...?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Hey...!」[k]
It is the voice from earlier! The voice, wherever it is coming from, echoes throughout the room.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Is there... someone there...?」[k]
[？？？ v=vp005 key=ポラリス f=polaris_99 buf=12]「I am Polaris, god of harmony.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Lady Polaris?!」[k]
Polaris, god of harmony. One of the four great gods who watch over this world.[k]
So, this voice is the voice of God?![k]
I never said I was a demon hunter, so that could very well be the case.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp006 f=polaris_99]「I have been waiting for you for a long time. You are a demon hunter, and I have been waiting for you to visit here.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp007 f=polaris_99]「I've been waiting for brave souls like you.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Me...?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp008 f=polaris_99]「Thank you for protecting the temple from the demons earlier. This is the only place where my voice can be heard by the people. Such an important place was about to be lost.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp009 f=polaris_99]「That demon you drove away just now is one of the senior demons who bring chaos to this world. Her name is Murmur.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Murmur...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp010 f=polaris_99]「Murmur is very magical and also very cunning. For the sake of world peace, she must not be left unchecked.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp011 f=polaris_99]「As you know, you have special powers. In order to fight that demon, your power as a demon hunter will be indispensable.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp012 f=polaris_99]「However she is a very high-ranking demon. To destroy her completely, your power alone will not be enough.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp013 f=polaris_99]「I, the God Polaris, need your help. Assist me in manifesting in this world.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Manifesting?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp014 f=polaris_99]「I reside in the world of gods. I cannot wield sufficient power as it is. For me to be powerful, I must descend to this world!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「So, what should I do...?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp015 f=polaris_99]「Collect 12 Magic Stones.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「12 Magic Stones?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp016 f=polaris_99]「Magic Stones are special gems that contain my divine power. Collecting them all can accomplish miracles!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp017 f=polaris_99]「Please visit here again after you have collected the 12 Magic Stones. Then I will be able to descend to earth.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「So, where are these Magic Stones?」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp018 f=polaris_99]「I do not know that. They were once enshrined in this temple, but over the last several hundred years, they have been pillaged.」[k]
[テオ f=09]「Oh, no...」[k]
So you're saying it's impossible to contain that demon...?[k]
[ポラリス v=vp019 f=polaris_99]「They are lost, but not destroyed. Although it is slight, I can sense the power of the twelve Magic Stones.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp020 f=polaris_99]「Some may not be far off. You simply need search for them.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
It's like trying to catch a cloud... finding a rock who knows where...[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Magic Stones. Well, I heard that someone I know has one in his possession.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Really?!」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp021 f=polaris_99]「Magic Stones are very beautiful and luminous gemstones, and are of incomparably higher value.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp022 f=polaris_99]「Therefore, the inhabitants of this world must be taking good care of them. You would not treat one roughly or throw it away.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「I have heard many rumors, not only from my acquaintances but also from others, of people possessing what may be Magic Stones. Following those rumors could well be valuable.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...Okay, I'll look for the 12 Magic Stones.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp023 f=polaris_99]「Thank you, demon hunting youth.」[k]
It's going to be a long job, but we can't leave the devil alone. I'll try my best somehow.[k]
Along with other adventures, I will try to gather information about the Magic Stones. I have to travel around as an adventurer anyway.[k]
If we persevere in gathering information, they should be discoverable over the course of our adventure.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp025 f=polaris_99]「Please observe the monument in front of you.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[textoff]
@reduceinfo
@image layer=4 storage="crystal_slot" left=227 top=102 visible=true
[texton w=2]
I look at the top of the monument.[k]
On it, several crystals were laid out in a circle.[k]
There were 12 crystals in total. This is consistent with the number of Magic Stones mentioned by the god Polaris.[k]
[ポラリス v=vp026]「Each of these crystals reacts and glows when a Magic Stone is brought close to it, if it is real.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp027]「In other words, when all these 12 crystals light up, I can descend unto this world.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp028]「Right now, not a single crystal is lit, but as you collect Magic Stones, the number of crystals that light up will gradually increase.」[k]
[ポラリス v=vp029]「Once you have collected all the Magic Stones, approach this monument again. Then I will be able to appear before you.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...Understood.」[k]
[textoff]
@layopt layer=4 left=0 top=0 visible=false
@w05
[texton w=0]
[ポラリス v=vp030 f=polaris_99]「Then I will return once more to the world of the gods. If you need anything else, please come back here and call on me.」[k]
[textoff]
@move layer=e0 time=500 path=,,0
@wm
@layopt layer=e0 opacity=255 visible=false
[texton]
The ambient light gradually faded, and the voice of Lady Polaris could no longer be longer heard.[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=シュバルツ f=00
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ f=00]「I know it's a lot of work, but this is a job that only you, a demon hunter, can do. I'm counting on you. I will help you as much as I can.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Yes, I will try my best.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Well, things are about to get busy...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What about you, Mr. Schwarz?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「I'm not retiring. We can't let that demon run wild, so I'll try to track it.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Okay... Please be careful.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=01]「Well, I'll leave you now. See you later, [テオ].」[k]
[textoff]
