After reporting to the princess, our party left the castle and walked along the main street of the town toward the inn.[k]
[   if exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve008 f=16]「Oh...? Something smells good.」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs009 f=16]「Oh...? Something smells good.」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM'][リム v=vh007 f=16]「Oh... Something smells good.」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd007 f=16]「Oh... Something smells good.」[k]
