[endif]
[テオ f=05]「Oh... Yes.」[k]
It sure smells good. It's a very sweet and fragrant smell.[k]
I looked around and saw a stall nearby selling apple pies. It seemed to be popular, as there were crowds of people around it.[k]
The apple pies were freshly baked and smelled delicious.[k]

@eval exp='tf.i = game.party.members.count - 1'
