[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Our members are staring at the pie stall as if entranced.[k]
[テオ f=02]「...Go ahead and eat if you want. I'll wait for you here.」[k]
[   if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh008 f=03]「Are you sure? Then I'll go!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd008 f=03]「Are you sure? Then I'll go!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve009 f=01]「Are you sure? Well, if it's okay.」[k]
