@se f=footstep2
The members trotted over to the stall, their eyes sparkling.[k]
...Girls really do have a sweet tooth, don't they?[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=リーゼル f=00
[texton w=1]
[リーゼル f=06]「...」[k]
That said, Riselle remained beside me.[k]
[テオ f=02]「You're not going?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl042 f=05]「I don't really like apple pie...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Oh, I see.」[k]
Well, everyone has a few likes and dislikes.[k]
[テオ f=12]「...」[k]
[リーゼル f=06]「...」[k]
Riselle and I wait there for the others to return, just the two of us.[k]
[テオ f=12]「...」[k]
[リーゼル f=06]「...」[k]
A long silence passes between us.[k]
It's rather awkward... let's talk about something.[k]
[テオ f=13]「H-hey, Riselle.」[k]
[リーゼル f=05]「...?」[k]
[テオ f=14]「You... always wear that hairpiece, don't you?」[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル f=05
[リーゼル v=vl043 f=05]「What... My hair ornament...?」[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル f=06
[リーゼル v=vl044 f=06]「U-uh, yes, but... is that odd?」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Oh, no! It's pretty and... I think it suits you.」[k]
I couldn't help but say something like that.[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル f=05
[リーゼル v=vl045 f=05]「Really?」[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル f=22
[リーゼル v=vl046 f=22]「Thank you, Captain... I'm glad...」[k]
Then Riselle gave a rare smile and looked genuinely happy.[k]
[テオ f=05]「...」[k]
I had never seen her like this before. I want her to like me, but I don't believe just a few words made her so happy...[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル f=01
[リーゼル v=vl047 f=01]「This hair ornament is a memento of my mother's.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?」[k]
You mean the mother who died when you were very young?[k]
[リーゼル v=vl048 f=01]「Originally, she wore it all the time, as a talisman for happiness...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「A good luck charm to make you happy...?」[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル f=02
[リーゼル v=vl049 f=02]「When I was five years old, my mother gave it to me. She said, "I'm happy enough, now you should be happy."」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl050 f=02]「My mother is gone, but I have this hair ornament. I feel like it's always protected me.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle...」[k]
So... it was precious to her. That's why she was so happy when I praised her hair ornament.[k]
[テオ f=02]「You... had a good mother.」[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル f=23
[リーゼル v=vl051 f=23]「...Yup!」[k]
Saying this, Riselle gave me a big smile.[k]
This was a new side of the uncommunicative Riselle. I felt as if I could see her true self and was secretly pleased.[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=witch_white_00]「Huh? That's never Riselle?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl052 f=05]「Aaa...」[k]
[textoff]
@cl b
@fg l=9005 top=50 b
@fg a=リーゼル left=768
[texton w=1]
Suddenly, a group of female adventurers walked toward us.[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=archer_purple_01]「Oh, it is. You're still in town, are you?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Are they old acquaintances of Riselle's? Despite that, she doesn't look too happy...[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=witch_white_00]「I wondered what you were gonna do when you said you were leaving our party. Looks like you're adventuring with this guy now～」[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=bladesman_black_06]「Well, I guess a newbie like you will get in trouble again with the new party and get kicked out anyway!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Apparently, they were members of Riselle's previous party.[k]
Maria said she often had bad experiences in the party and didn't get much of a share of the reward...[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=witch_white_00]「Hey, you, come back to our party.」[k]
@fgf a=リーゼル f=09 left=768
[リーゼル v=vl053 f=09]「Ehh...」[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=archer_purple_01]「Yeah, surely there's some use we can find for you again! Ahahahahaha!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
They're clearly mocking Riselle. She's completely deflated.[k]
...I have to stop this...![k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=witch_white_00]「Join us again. We'll forgive you if you apologize right here. But we'd still have to pay you a lousy share ♪」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl054 f=09]「Let's see... well...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle will not be returning to your party.」[k]
I intervened between the girls.[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=bladesman_black_00]「Huh? Who are you?」[k]
@fgf a=リーゼル f=25 left=768
[リーゼル v=vl055 f=25]「Captain...!」[k]
I can't stand by and watch any longer. I am the captain. I have to protect my party.[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=witch_white_00]「Oh, maybe you're the leader of Riselle's new party?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle is an important member of our party. We will never give her up.」[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=witch_white_00]「Ohh? Ohhh? That's cool, Captain!」[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=archer_purple_01]「You say that, but you'll end up kicking that liability out eventually.」[k]
[テオ f=07]「Riselle is not a liability! She's an indispensable member of our party.」[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=witch_white_00]「That sounds so nice～ good, good!」[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=bladesman_black_01]「What? Are you in love with her?」[k]
[テオ f=26]「No, no, I never meant...」[k]
[name n="Female Adventurer" f=witch_white_00]「Oh～ oh～ he's turning red.」[k]
