[textoff]
@clf
; 回復とレベルアップ
@call storage="anime.ks" target=*fountain_star
@eventsleep effect=false
@changefloor pimg=human
@fgf c=priest_purple_nude left=450
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=01]「Thanks, I feel all better.」[k]
[少女 f=priest_purple_02]「If you need to be healed again, you're welcome to come back here.」[k]
[少女 f=priest_purple_02]「We have a sister of the Aura Church here too. She's well versed in various treatments, so please let her know if you need anything.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「All right. Well, I'm off.」[k]
[少女 f=priest_purple_02]「Adventurers, please be careful.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
[eventoff cond='game.notPlayInFullVersion']
[texton w=0]
The fate of not only ourselves, but the former prisoners, rests on our shoulders. We will find a way out, no matter what it takes.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl064 f=93]「...It's gone!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What's wrong?」[k]
Suddenly, Riselle sounded very anxious.[k]
[テオ f=05]「What's wrong? What's gone?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl065 f=93]「My hair ornament... My mother's hair ornament is missing...!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What?!」[k]
Riselle lost the hair accessory she loves so much? Could it have been when she fell down the hole earlier?![k]
[ムールムール v=vm071 f=03]「Gahahahaha!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...!」[k]
[textoff]
@se f=wing2
@fg c=8003 left=440 top=-30
[texton w=0]
Suddenly, Murmur's voice echoed from the sky above.[k]
[テオ f=07]「Devil! You're still there?!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm072 f=02]「This is what you're looking for, right?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl066 f=93]「Ah...!」[k]
[name f=other_01]Murmur held Riselle's hair ornament. Gliding out of reach, she showed it off.[k]
[ムールムール v=vm073 f=15]「Your hair ornament is pretty, so I think I'll keep it! See you～!」[k]
[textoff]
@se f=wing3
@cl
[texton w=0]
∗flap!∗ ∗flap!∗[k]
[リーゼル v=vl067 f=93]「Wait, wait...!」[k]
[テオ f=07]「Wait! Devil! Give it back!」[k]
Our calls were in vain, and Murmur flew away with the hair ornament in her hand.[k]
Damn... That devil...! She even stole Riselle's precious hair ornament...[k]
[リーゼル v=vl068 f=10]「...I'll never get my hair ornament back...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「That's not true. I'll get it back someday...」[k]
I tried to put her mind at ease for now, but honestly, it seemed unlikely.[k]
[リーゼル f=10]「...」[k]
Riselle looks completely depressed.[k]
[テオ f=10]「Anyway, our first priority now is to escape. If we get out of here, then maybe we can find a way to get it back.」[k]
[リーゼル f=10]「...∗nod∗」[k]
Riselle's expression remained gloomy. But for the sake of the other party members and the girls who are being held captive, we have to put it behind us for now.[k]
Damn you devil...! Just how much trouble do you have to cause us before you're satisfied...?![k]
[textoff]

; ヘッドレスに捕まった時に途中で解放されるかどうか
@eval exp='f.safeReturnFromHeadless = true'

[eventoff]


;◇イベント05・レッサーデビル再戦・事件解決
*labyrinth_5

; ☆フリーモード
@jump storage="free01.scn" target=*labyrinth_5 cond='game.isFreeMode && ! game.notPlayInFullVersion'

; 古代の迷宮・入口の部屋
@fg c=devil_yellow left=450 top=-15
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Hey! Lesser Devil!」[k]
[name n="Lesser Devil" f=devil_00]「What?」[k]
[name n="Lesser Devil" f=devil_00]「Y-you guys...?! How the hell did you get out of that labyrinth?!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「This time I will defeat you! I won't let you kidnap more girls!」[k]
[name n="Lesser Devil" f=devil_00]「Damn...! If that's how it is, I'll do whatever it takes to take you guys down! Hey, guys, gather round!」[k]
At the order of Lesser Devil, his minions gathered from all over the place. The other side was also fighting with all its might.[k]
It's time to end this. We need to save the girls in the labyrinth![k]
[textoff]
@clf

; 再びレッサーデビルと戦闘
@monster pos=1 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=2 name=スケルトンガード
@monster pos=4 name=スケルトンガード
@monster pos=5 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=10 name=レッサーデビル
@callbattle bgm=boss escape=false gameover=true

; 勝利
[texton]
[テオ f=01]「Alright! We finally beat the Lesser Devil! This incident is now resolved!」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=500
@saveon
[texton]
Having defeated the enemy, we lowered a rope ladder into the underground room and succeeded in rescuing all the girls.[k]
We then returned safely to the village with the rescued girls.[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@eval exp='game.view.close()'
@eval exp='game.openTownView(o.シーガルの村)'
@gameon

; シーガルの村
@mu f=beach
[texton]
[name n=Villager]「Thank you! Thank you so much!」[k]
[name n=Villager]「It is truly a dream come true to see my daughter again. How can I ever thank you guys enough...」[k]
The villagers greeted us with a huge ovation.[k]
[name n="Village Chief" f=mayor_01]「You guys have been such a great help. This is just a small thank you from the villagers. Please accept it.」[k]
[textoff]
@complete name=さらわれた少女たちの救出
@treasure item=エメラルドの魔石

[texton]
[テオ f=05]「This is the magic stone...!」[k]
[name f=other_05]It was a beautiful jewel with a green glow.[k]
[name f=other_05]Unlike an ordinary gemstone, the light of magic flickers inside it, illuminating its surroundings with a subtle green light.[k]
[name n="Village Chief" f=mayor_02]「Do you know anything about magic stones?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Yes. Actually, I'm collecting these magic stones for a reason...」[k]
I told the Seagull Village chief about what had happened at the Temple of Polaris.[k]
[name n="Village Chief" f=mayor_02]「I see, that was the situation...! To defeat the demons that threaten the world...!」[k]
[name n="Village Chief" f=mayor_01]「Since that is the case, I am even more glad that I was able to give you the magic stone. Please use it for the good of the world.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes, thank you.」[k]
[name n="Village Chief" f=mayor_02]「Well, I guess we'll leave it at that.」[k]
[name n="Village Chief" f=mayor_01]「We have prepared a banquet for you, our village's heroes. Please enjoy yourselves to the fullest this evening.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=500
@jump target=*labyrinth_end_after_skip_prologue cond='game.notPlayInFullVersion'

@bg f=0020
@mu f=happy
[texton w=1]
That evening, a party was held in the square of Seagull Village for us.[k]
The villagers prepared many treats and we received generous hospitality.[k]
It was very enjoyable, full of the laughter of the villagers. Seeing the villagers dancing happily around the bonfire, I was truly happy to have accomplished this quest.[k]
[テオ e=通常 f=02]「You look unhappy, Riselle.」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル e=通常・大 f=10
[リーゼル v=vl069 f=10]「Y-yeah...」[k]
While the other party members were happily eating and dancing, Riselle was the only one looking downcast.[k]
[テオ f=05]「...Your hair ornament?」[k]
[リーゼル f=10]「...」[k]
It was a precious memento from her mother, so she must still be in shock.[k]
[テオ f=02]「It might not be gone forever. If we can follow that demon's tracks, we might find it again.」[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル e=通常・大 f=05
[リーゼル v=vl070 f=05]「Do you really think so...?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I can't say for sure, but we might if we keep looking. I'll look for it with you, so let's not give up yet.」[k]
[リーゼル f=05]「...」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル e=通常・大 f=02
[リーゼル v=vl071 f=02]「...Yeah, okay. I'll do my best to find it.」[k]
Finally, she smiled a little.[k]
@fg c=リーゼル e=通常・大 f=01
[リーゼル v=vl072 f=01]「Thank you, Captain. I knew you were kind.」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Oh, no... 」[k]
I'm embarrassed to hear Riselle say that again...[k]
[テオ f=01]「That's right! Hey, Riselle. Do you want to dance?」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル e=通常・大 f=25
[リーゼル v=vl073 f=25]「Eh...」[k]
@fg c=リーゼル e=通常・大 f=22
[リーゼル v=vl074 f=22]「Yeah... that's fine. If it's with you...」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Well, let's go!」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
[texton]
I took Riselle's hand and we joined the dancing circle of villagers.[k]
I hold Riselle's small hands and stand in front of her. Our faces are close, facing each other head-on.[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=リーゼル e=通常・大 f=21
[texton]
[リーゼル v=vl075 f=21]「Ahaha... I'm a little embarrassed... 」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Let's forget about the bad stuff today and have fun.」[k]
We were feeling the warmth of each other's hands as we took somewhat awkward steps.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@wait time=500

@eventsleep
@wait time=500
@addevent name=サファイアシティ num=3
@delevent map=古代の迷宮Ｂ２ num=3
@delevent map=古代の迷宮Ｂ２ num=4
@changefloor map=古代の迷宮Ｂ２ x=6 y=2 pimg=void
@changefloor map=古代の迷宮Ｂ２ x=0 y=3 pimg=void
@eval exp='o.リーゼル.moveHeart(o.テオ, 10)'
@jump target=*trial_version_end cond='isDemoVersion'
@eval exp='game.openTownView(o.シーガルの村)'
@jump target=*past_episode_from_demo cond='! f.readPastEpisode'
[eventoff bgm]



;■体験版の通常ストーリー終了
*trial_version_end

@out
@wait time=500
[texton w=0]
After this, there were twists and turns. Riselle left the party, and Max rejoined.[k]
From here on, you will be able to play freely, which is only available in the trial version. Choose your own quests and explore the dungeons freely.[k]
Note that the maximum level is [b][emb exp='game.levelCapOnDemo'][/b] and maximum magic level is [b][emb exp='game.magicLevelCapOnDemo'][/b].[r]
Also, there is no ending.[k]
[b][nw]※Note[r]
Please note that if you save your game from this point, you will not be able to import the save into the commercial version, so use a different file.[r]
(Characters and items can be imported into new games.)[k]
[textoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[iscript]

o.マックス.dressEquipment(o.硬い革鎧);
o.マックス.dressEquipment(o.布のズボン);
o.マックス.dressEquipment(o.冒険者のパンツ);
o.リーゼル.storeAllItemsInOthers();
game.party.removeMember(o.リーゼル);
game.party.entry(o.マックス);
game.guest.entry(o.ライナス);
game.guest.entry(o.ミレディ);

o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.remove(o.ポラリス神殿を守ってほしい);
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.remove(o.盗賊メンバー派遣の依頼);
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.add(o.コボルド退治);
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.add(o.スライム軍団の討伐);
o.盗賊メンバー派遣の依頼.complete();

o.ランドン渓谷・崖上.events.add(7);
game.notPlayInFullVersion = true;	// ここから先は製品版での継続不可

// 移動制限
o.サファイアシティ・南東門.events = [6];
o.シーガルの村・東門.events = [2];
o.コリンズの森.events.push2(19);
o.コリンズの森.events.remove(10);
o.ランドン渓谷・谷底.events.push2(4);
o.フーラ雪原・南の森.events.push2(10);
o.ヤネクの森・霧の谷.events.push2(5);

// その他
f.safeReturnFromHeadless = false;
f.heroineEventProgress = true;
game.lovers.add(o.ライナス);

[endscript]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@eval exp='game.enterTown(o.シーガルの村, o.かもめ亭, true)'
[eventoff]




;■体験版でプロローグスキップした場合   ※無しになった
*labyrinth_end_after_skip_prologue
@eventsleep
@wait time=500
@delevent map=古代の迷宮Ｂ２ num=3
@delevent map=古代の迷宮Ｂ２ num=4
@changefloor map=古代の迷宮Ｂ２ x=6 y=2 pimg=void
@changefloor map=古代の迷宮Ｂ２ x=1 y=3 pimg=void
@eval exp='game.enterTown(o.シーガルの村, o.かもめ亭, true)'
[eventoff]




;■体験版で語られなかったエピソード
; 体験版でスキップしなかった場合でもブルーとの過去やムールムールとの初対面は
; 描かれないので、ここで改めて描く

*past_episode_from_demo
@gameon fade
@w1
[texton w=0]
[テオ e=通常 f=02]「...」[k]
I've managed to get back on track. So far so good.[k]
When I think back to a year ago, things have gone incredibly well. Yes, compared to the time when I was under Blue's control...[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Blue. He's a scary guy. Max and I were in despair for a while after getting involved with him.[k]
That was why Max and I had to escape Bravetown.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1
[texton]
A year ago in Bravetown...[k]
As a new adventurer, I was full of hope for the life of adventure that was about to begin.[k]
[textoff]
@w1
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[iscript]

for(var i = game.party.members.count - 1; i >= 0; i--)
{
	var one = game.party.members[i];
	if(one == game.playerChara) continue;
	game.removeMemberTemporary(one);
}
game.party.entry(o.マックス);
o.テオ.storeAllItemsInOthers(game.temporaryBox);
o.テオ.dressEquipment(o.布の服);
o.テオ.dressEquipment(o.トランクス);
o.テオ.dressEquipment(o.ショートソード);
o.テオ.makeBustups();

o.冒険者ギルド.visible = o.冒険者ギルド.appeared = false;
o.ホテル琥珀.visible = o.ホテル琥珀.appeared = false;
o.冒険者の保管庫.visible = o.冒険者の保管庫.appeared = false;
o.ブレイブタウン・西門.visible = o.ブレイブタウン・西門.appeared = false;
o.自宅.visible = o.自宅.appeared = true;

game.lapse = false;
game.openTownView(o.ブレイブタウン);

[endscript]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@jump storage="main02.scn" target=*_past_1_from_demo




; 回想から戻る
*return_from_past_episode

; 夕方・町の出口
@saveon
@out
@w05
@bg f=0017
[texton w=1]
That evening...[k]
After preparing for the trip in a great hurry, Max, Mr. Schwartz, and I prepared to stealthily leave.[k]
Fortunately, we weren't found by Blue's gang and were able to get out of town safely.[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「You're both ready. Let's go!」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes!」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Yeah!」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1

[texton w=0]
Then Max and I headed for Sapphire City under the guidance of Mr. Schwartz.[k]
Along the way, we reunited with Maria and Riselle, and despite being hindered by Alex, we manage to reach Sapphire City without being found by Blue's gang.[k]
I gathered some new companions and began my life as an adventurer anew.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
After Blue, I'd given up on a life as an adventurer, but that relationship has now come to an end.[k]
This time, I will walk my ideal path of becoming an adventurer.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1

;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; 設定
[iscript]

// 修正
o.森の中の廃屋入口.events = [];
o.町外れの遺跡入口.events = [];

// 体験版からの縛り外し
o.サファイアシティ・南東門.events = [];
o.シーガルの村・東門.events = [];
o.ノームの洞窟.events.push2(1);
o.ヤネクの森・霧の谷.events.remove(5);

// 本筋に戻る
game.party.removeMember(o.マックス);
game.restoreMembers();
game.lapse = true;
game.gameFrame.updateClock();
game.enterTown(o.シーガルの村, o.かもめ亭, true);

[endscript]
;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[eventoff]

